sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Resend as Resend (Email)
    
    User->>Frontend: Input Registration Data (Email/Password)
    Frontend->>Backend: Submit Registration Request
    Backend->>Backend: Create Inactive Account
    Backend->>Resend: Trigger 6-digit OTP Email
    Resend-->>User: Deliver OTP Email
    User->>Frontend: Input 6-digit OTP
    Frontend->>Backend: Verify OTP Request
    Backend->>Backend: Validate OTP & Activate Account
    Backend-->>Frontend: Verification Success
    Frontend-->>User: Redirect to Main Dashboard
    
    note over User,Resend: Forgot Password Flow
    User->>Frontend: Request Forgot Password
    Frontend->>Backend: Send Email for Reset
    Backend->>Resend: Send Secure Reset Link & OTP
    Resend-->>User: Deliver Reset Link (Expires 15m)
